# Git LFS — Unity native plugins
#
# Stored on forgejo.kbve.com/KBVE/rareicon.git via the .lfsconfig
# endpoint. Pointer files (text, ~150 bytes) live in this GitHub repo;
# real binaries live on the self-hosted Forgejo LFS.
#
# Pattern coverage:
#   - libuniti.dylib  (Rust FFI shared library, macOS)
#   - uniti.dll       (Rust FFI shared library, Windows)
#   - libuniti.so     (Rust FFI shared library, Linux)
#   - any future native plugin under apps/rareicon/**/Plugins/**
apps/rareicon/**/Plugins/**/*.dylib filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
apps/rareicon/**/Plugins/**/*.dll   filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
apps/rareicon/**/Plugins/**/*.so    filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
